snippet.title: World Map Quiz   promo video
snippet.description:
Download for free for android!

Do you know where Monaco lies? Yes? Great! Take the challenge and find other countries. No? No worries! Learn geography with us!

With World Map Quiz you can enjoy learning locations of all countries around the World.

Discover new challenges during playing in flag and capital mode. Try to prove yourself in extraordinary elimination mode. 

Just download it and have fun!
